# Radio — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/radio.css`

## CSS Classes

### Group
- `.acko-radio-group` — flex column, gap-2
- `.acko-radio-group-label` — label-lg typography
- `.acko-radio-options` — flex container
- `.acko-radio-vertical` / `.acko-radio-horizontal` — orientation

### Item (default variant)
- `.acko-radio-item` — inline-flex, items-start, gap-3, cursor-pointer
- `.acko-radio-item-selected` — selected state
- `.acko-radio-item-disabled` — disabled state
- `.acko-radio-error` — error state

### Circle + Dot
- `.acko-radio-circle` — border 2px `--color-control-border-selector`, rounded-full
- `.acko-radio-dot` — inner dot, animated bounce on selection

### Sizes (via `.acko-radio-{size}`)
| Size | Circle | Dot | Label Font |
|------|--------|-----|------------|
| sm | `--scale-16` | `--scale-8` | `--font-body-sm-size` |
| md | `--scale-20` | `--scale-10` | `--font-body-md-size` |
| lg | `--scale-24` | `--scale-12` | `--font-body-lg-size` |

### Card Variant
- `.acko-radio-card-item` — border, rounded-3xl, padding, card-bg
- Uses `--color-radio-card-*` tokens for hover/active states

### States (raw CSS)
- Selected: circle fills `--color-primary`, scale(1.08)
- Hover: `@media (hover:hover)` — muted border, subtle bg
- Focus: `box-shadow: --shadow-focus-ring` via `:focus-visible`
- Disabled: subtle border, raised bg, muted text
- Error: error border color
